response.overview: The queen of misanthropy gifts us her inspiring origin story as a performer. And obliterates the middle classes, Air Fryer owners and parents who bring their kids into pubs along the way. Rachel,'very much the rock'n'roll star of British comedy' (Rolling Stone), is back with her critically acclaimed hour Showgirl. She'll be casting her acerbic eye over everything from your children to her pretentious new alcohol-free life (accurate at time of writing).
response.title: Rachel Fairburn: Showgirl
